{"tid":2305111,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【緊急】唔好捐錢比呢位手足！！！！！！！！！","createTime":"2020-11-29T10:59:36.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-29T13:38:18.000Z","uid":79793,"like":24,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"99d1a56f7ff704a6ae23bcaec79f25e7bbd2b095","tid":2305111,"uid":79793,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-29T10:59:36.000Z","msg":"［緊急］呢個女仔比狗踢到有創傷後遺症<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/aGcabpU\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/aGcabpU</a><br />\n<br />\n呢個女仔係柴灣比人放上網話差人十幾萬<br />\n身邊全部同學朋友都比佢問過借錢未還<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1ih0w4M.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1ih0w4M.png&h=4478405b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/r0h4ehi.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fr0h4ehi.png&h=8d675371&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"gold\">佢跑幾秒都跑唔郁，點樣做前線啊<br />\n同埋我係跟柴灣議員一齊睇黎明行動嘅，果幾日都冇見過呢條女係柴灣上前<br />\n基本上柴灣前線大家都識大家，有班係由細玩到大，但係從未見過佢上前</span></span><br />\n<br />\n手足就一定係，佢絕對係黃絲係和理非，但係佢個名係柴灣好臭<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4bdfeebf207649073918a2a063a50f2a546460fc","tid":2305111,"uid":116696,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-29T11:01:17.000Z","msg":"冇錢醫病喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"68af54371568a05f9726b9d3095c679cce5e5931","tid":2305111,"uid":79793,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"4bdfeebf207649073918a2a063a50f2a546460fc","tid":2305111,"uid":116696,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-29T11:01:17.000Z","msg":"冇錢醫病喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-29T11:02:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4WVhzhC.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4WVhzhC.png&h=76333d32&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"bad718280e315a27a8a804523e85094be41e8856","tid":2305111,"uid":167928,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-29T11:03:02.000Z","msg":"但係佢嘅傷勢係點嚟？佢有冇受傷？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eff3f1cab303b2c6025cb5e008f6dff2a95e3b6b","tid":2305111,"uid":4574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-29T11:06:21.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"523bd2549925927da2547f52277d77abc445665f","tid":2305111,"uid":158635,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-29T11:08:39.000Z","msg":"依家睇post真係要等埋反轉先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"10dd33fab9af2d4de0a2329015453eaadd5d4266","tid":2305111,"uid":297453,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-29T11:09:31.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"79a729694458bb323a41a7c230d4891275aa0554","tid":2305111,"uid":59976,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-29T11:15:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://media.whatscap.com/a70/d96/a70d960e8621e1bad2d4cfd34db47a8fbe248e26_n.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.whatscap.com%2Fa70%2Fd96%2Fa70d960e8621e1bad2d4cfd34db47a8fbe248e26_n.jpg&h=4590078c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2ea5fc80554af7c245c0c406d87987613a458d42","tid":2305111,"uid":79117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-29T11:17:16.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"80b140fe1434e3bb51573457305932949a6b442f","tid":2305111,"uid":51469,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-29T11:18:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/rubbish.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2fb031a36019990f48e8100a339d6bbdd65b010f","tid":2305111,"uid":187664,"like":0,"d